description: A fully object-oriented .Net wrapper for the TrelloAPI.
releaseNotes:
WARNING: This release contains many breaking changes, but is remarkably faster than v0.6.9.  The previous versions will remain available for some time.  Please be sure to read the wiki pages at https://bitbucket.org/gregsdennis/manatee.trello/wiki/Home.

See Trello board for this project at https://trello.com/b/BVlClkAR/.  Feedback and questions are welcome through the board, on StackOverflow, or by emailing littlecrabsolutions@yahoo.com.

v1.0
Refactored to include a new synchronization framework supporting all entities.
Removed TrelloService in favor of direct object instantiation.
Drastically reduced call frequency by:
 - utilizing all of the data received from the API,
 - consolidating multiple updates into a single call after a configurable idle time, and
 - sending only data changes, not entire objects.
Exposed collection properties as specific collection classes to allow direct modification.
Changes are tracked so that incoming updates do not overwrite unsubmitted changes.
Caching is more reliable.
All objects now expose an Updated event.
title: Manatee.Trello
